de.loki.metallum.entity.Band.name: Drudkh
de.loki.metallum.entity.Band.lyricalThemes: Nature, Ukrainian History, Folklore and Poetry
de.loki.metallum.entity.Band.info:
On some of their albums Drudkh uses the lyrics of Taras Shevchenko and other Ukrainian poets.
Drudkh means "wood" in Romanised Sanskrit.
Drudkh doesn't support any extreme ideology and declares itself as a non-political band.
Thurios is the owner of Stuza Production.
